Job Responsibilities
 Front-desk duties;
 Attend walk-in customers;
 Administrative Support Duties;
 Basic operations work;
 Sales order processing
 Handling customer enquiries and issues;
 Ad-hoc duties as assigned.
Our Ideal Customer Service Executive
 Has an energetic and cheerful personality with excellent professionalism;
 Is a good team player;
 Is fluent in English (Written and Spoken);
 Is proficient in Mandarin (This would be advantageous, in order to handle enquires from Mandarin-speaking customers);
 Possesses basic Microsoft Office Skills;
 Has an organised and meticulous working style.
Entry level candidates are also welcomed, as training will be provided.
Able to work on alternate Saturday.